📌 Fitness Force — AI Exercise Form Detection

Fitness Force is an AI-powered fitness form correction system that analyzes workout videos and detects whether exercises are performed correctly or incorrectly. It supports Squat, Bicep Curl, Lunge, and Plank using pose estimation and deep learning.


🚀 Features

MediaPipe Pose (33 landmarks) for pose extraction
107-feature biomechanical representation (coords + angles)
60-frame sliding windows
CNN + GRU hybrid deep-learning model
Detects correct form & specific mistakes
Flask web app for video upload and results
Works on any camera or pre-recorded videos


🧠 Model Overview

CNN + GRU Hybrid
CNN → local movement patterns (elbow/hip/knee motion)
GRU → long-term sequence understanding (full rep behavior)
Dense layers → classify correct vs incorrect form